name: Coadjutor to the Stars.
description: A single-player/cooperative map. Mainly, a space- base theme with a quarry and some nukage to even it out. Something I made in my spare time with no real intent on winning the "Best Level of the Year" award. Though, I just wanted something fun to play! Play this one several times, there are many secrets to find! I sometimes don't even find them all when I play, and I made it!
